{"tid":972772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★六旬女工麥頌崎猝死遺體無人領　同事憂淪無主孤魂代尋親","createTime":"2019-01-07T15:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T08:48:30.000Z","uid":19454,"like":156,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"8f10e68deda2d35fdf1e189f9de7a3a6a86c1474","tid":972772,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:15:03.000Z","msg":"任職公立醫院清潔工、60多歲的麥頌崎在去年11月上旬，乘小巴上班途中不省人事，急救未幾即告猝死。面對共事多年的好同事溘然而逝，於同一醫院工作的李小姐，得悉麥頌崎的遺體至今仍無人認領，亦曾多番嘗試聯絡其家人不果，她擔心若無人認領麥女遺體，她將要長埋沙嶺公墓，成為無名無姓孤魂，遂「拍心口」希望代領遺體。但由於她並非麥的親人，亦未獲授權，故不得要領。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">生前形單影隻　死後無親人認屍</span><br />\n<br />\n麥女全名麥頌崎，生前於瑪嘉烈醫院擔任清潔工，年資逾10年。李小姐是麥女的醫院同事，雖然並非同一部門，但兩人經常有講有笑，可算熟稔；李小姐亦不時於屋企附近餐廳偶遇麥女，但每次均見她形單影隻。<br />\n<br />\n去年11月上旬，麥女於清早乘車上班途中突然暈倒，並送至瑪嘉烈急救，惟最後證實不治。當天返夜班的李小姐憶述，自己收工時，赫見麥女被送至急症室，原以為搶救成功，詎料事隔數小時，麥已不幸離世。她又提到，麥女生前患有哮喘，曾因氣管收縮被要求留醫，但麥拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n由於麥離世後，遺體一直未有親人認領，李小姐事後曾前往麥女生前居住的公屋單位「拍門」，但無人應門，又試過翻閱其手機電話簿，亦未能尋獲其親屬聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n李小姐指，據了解麥女單身未嫁，但過往於言談間，曾提及自己有同住的親人，「佢話屋企有個人。」惟至今亦未有任何親屬前來認領遺體，她大感奇怪，亦為麥女憂心着急：「如果過了3個月無人認領，就要送去公眾殮房，好殘忍。」李小姐遂與同事發起網上尋親，但至今未有任何音訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/279588/%E5%B0%8B%E8%A6%AA-%E5%85%AD%E6%97%AC%E5%A5%B3%E5%B7%A5%E9%BA%A5%E9%A0%8C%E5%B4%8E%E7%8C%9D%E6%AD%BB%E9%81%BA%E9%AB%94%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E9%A0%98-%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8B%E6%86%82%E6%B7%AA%E7%84%A1%E4%B8%BB%E5%AD%A4%E9%AD%82%E4%BB%A3%E5%B0%8B%E8%A6%AA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F279588%2F%25E5%25B0%258B%25E8%25A6%25AA-%25E5%2585%25AD%25E6%2597%25AC%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E9%25A0%258C%25E5%25B4%258E%25E7%258C%259D%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E9%2581%25BA%25E9%25AB%2594%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%25A0%2598-%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BA%258B%25E6%2586%2582%25E6%25B7%25AA%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25AD%25A4%25E9%25AD%2582%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E5%25B0%258B%25E8%25A6%25AA&d=eWF3JVrZtYO%2BsRPnNlRqME%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=196b1cfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/279588/%E5%B0%8B%E8%A6%AA-%E5%85%AD%E6%97%AC%E5%A5%B3%E5%B7%A5%E9%BA%A5%E9%A0%8C%E5%B4%8E%E7%8C%9D%E6%AD%BB%E9%81%BA%E9%AB%94%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E9%A0%98-%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8B%E6%86%82%E6%B7%AA%E7%84%A1%E4%B8%BB%E5%AD%A4%E9%AD%82%E4%BB%A3%E5%B0%8B%E8%A6%AA</a>"},{"pid":"7441f03b3ce7f02619a7b110f13410d54236b9a6","tid":972772,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:15:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30fb45e974529d7cbc51509187d24663d44a0ff","tid":972772,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"716f02fb0e5c03bac369f5b14b26afc9fb0a2fa0","tid":972772,"uid":19454,"like":19,"dislike":5,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:16:08.000Z","msg":"毒撚的未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb7af30cbd9dc41e3c14167116568dbd2b185e4","tid":972772,"uid":14983,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37682a10bafb81da28da76a22a15a5aa0fb5a49","tid":972772,"uid":19454,"like":168,"dislike":1,"score":167,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:17:37.000Z","msg":"Lihkg毒撚未來會在沙嶺公墓相聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5d5e182c201a15a7c6e57d698c2d29a395c0dcb","tid":972772,"uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"c37682a10bafb81da28da76a22a15a5aa0fb5a49","tid":972772,"uid":19454,"like":168,"dislike":1,"score":167,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:17:37.000Z","msg":"Lihkg毒撚未來會在沙嶺公墓相聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:18:53.000Z","msg":"無人認領遺體或長埋沙嶺公墓<br />\n<br />\n曾為不少長者及露宿者代辦身後事的社區組織協會幹事吳衛東指，由他人代領遺體程序較為困難，但並非不可，因醫院一般會轉介至警方處理，如未有親人認領，代領者需經多重認證，他過往曾為機構受助者代辦身後事，如有紀錄證明，所需時間較快。他又指，遺體會隨擺放時間出現變化，亦會影響容貌，建議如情況許可，應盡快領取。"},{"pid":"ba5434b7d78f5c058ef3be1b77ca3c3a7fe79f47","tid":972772,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c37682a10bafb81da28da76a22a15a5aa0fb5a49","tid":972772,"uid":19454,"like":168,"dislike":1,"score":167,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:17:37.000Z","msg":"Lihkg毒撚未來會在沙嶺公墓相聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:21:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f627bda2136a64b41bb24ea2c17ba8ccab8372b6","tid":972772,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:23:23.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"8fbbbb35e123212ceee780bd6b90d6d225877670","tid":972772,"uid":41821,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:23:27.000Z","msg":"好似得個number<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3da180e8ac45713ec24517c8cc2906efe62be63","tid":972772,"uid":11148,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:27:33.000Z","msg":"李小姐事後曾前往麥女生前居住的公屋單位「拍門」，<span style=\"color: red;\">但無人應門，又試過翻閱其手機電話簿，亦未能尋獲其親屬聯絡</span>。<br />\n<br />\n李小姐指，據了解麥女單身未嫁，但過往於言談間，曾提及自己有同住的親人，「<span style=\"color: red;\">佢話屋企有個人</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n人係邊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f174bb5ac703ac0af598f90b8d722eae5cc60b0","tid":972772,"uid":51920,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:30:35.000Z","msg":"有私樓就會有班親戚搶住認"},{"pid":"7f25a0c084bde41318bef85bf0ac08e59e7490e6","tid":972772,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":