E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F279588%2F%E5%B0%8B%E8%A6%AA-%E5%85%AD%E6%97%AC%E5%A5%B3%E5%B7%A5%E9%BA%A5%E9%A0%8C%E5%B4%8E%E7%8C%9D%E6%AD%BB%E9%81%BA%E9%AB%94%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E9%A0%98-%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8B%E6%86%82%E6%B7%AA%E7%84%A1%E4%B8%BB%E5%AD%A4%E9%AD%82%E4%BB%A3%E5%B0%8B%E8%A6%AA&d=eWF3JVrZtYO%2BsRPnNlRqME%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=18a06d70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/279588/尋親-六旬女工麥頌崎猝死遺體無人領-同事憂淪無主孤魂代尋親</a>"},{"pid":"ff0f9ec1b2555ceb1b266af79e05d9ee78dd1f68","tid":972772,"uid":26306,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T16:38:24.000Z","msg":"點解唔係班仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8cc651f9140222343cb2305fdd68e1b8ca130ba","tid":972772,"uid":1886,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T16:42:03.000Z","msg":"黃土上，亂草叢，密麻麻東歪西倒小石碑，沒名沒姓，只有一組號碼，猶如亂葬崗。目睹此情此景，人馬上長大，大家嚷着不想孤單的葬在公墓；從死到生，大家感受活着的幸福，自毀非解脫，只會帶來身邊親人永不磨滅的哀痛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20160404/large/04la2p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20160404%2Flarge%2F04la2p2.jpg&h=157dc511&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公墓分棺木及骨灰兩大區，分佈不同山頭。棺木區只見一個個荒涼山頭，密麻麻一個個小石碑，碑上只刻有安葬年份及一個代表死者的號碼，沒名沒姓沒遺照，沒一束花，只得𤏸土雜草，和一群餓瘋了的蚊。棺木葬了7年後，需起出來火化，並放在另一邊山頭的骨灰區，「火化咗之後，唔會逐個分，會將同一年嘅骨灰放埋一齊」死亡學院士梁梓敦道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20160404/19556817\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20160404%2F19556817&d=eWF3JVrZtYO%2BsRPnNlRqME%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=d5b83d8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20160404%2F19556817&h=114db9a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20160404/19556817</a>"},{"pid":"5465c9012d6ca92963ef95ca58c93d7ddf2d4989","tid":972772,"uid":130105,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1398e945f08833227a9ac6e3dd30daad6bf45d26","tid":972772,"uid":19454,"like":124,"dislike":0,"score":124,"quote":{"pid":"d3da180e8ac45713ec24517c8cc2906efe62be63","tid":972772,"uid":11148,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:27:33.000Z","msg":"李小姐事後曾前往麥女生前居住的公屋單位「拍門」，<span style=\"color: red;\">但無人應門，又試過翻閱其手機電話簿，亦未能尋獲其親屬聯絡</span>。<br />\n<br />\n李小姐指，據了解麥女單身未嫁，但過往於言談間，曾提及自己有同住的親人，「<span style=\"color: red;\">佢話屋企有個人</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n人係邊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T15:55:38.000Z","msg":"同事間閒談，講d嘢有幾多9up，心照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T16:46:50.000Z","msg":"定係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a2ebcd18bad0006e04db19d8cb9461d44838c0","tid":972772,"uid":19454,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"a8cc651f9140222343cb2305fdd68e1b8ca130ba","tid":972772,"uid":1886,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T16:42:03.000Z","msg":"黃土上，亂草叢，密麻麻東歪西倒小石碑，沒名沒姓，只有一組號碼，猶如亂葬崗。目睹此情此景，人馬上長大，大家嚷着不想孤單的葬在公墓；從死到生，大家感受活着的幸福，自毀非解脫，只會帶來身邊親人永不磨滅的哀痛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20160404/large/04la2p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20160404%2Flarge%2F04la2p2.jpg&h=157dc511&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公墓分棺木及骨灰兩大區，分佈不同山頭。棺木區只見一個個荒涼山頭，密麻麻一個個小石碑，碑上只刻有安葬年份及一個代表死者的號碼，沒名沒姓沒遺照，沒一束花，只得𤏸土雜草，和一群餓瘋了的蚊。棺木葬了7年後，需起出來火化，並放在另一邊山頭的骨灰區，「火化咗之後，唔會逐個分，會將同一年嘅骨灰放埋一齊」死亡學院士梁梓敦道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/artic